article.headline: Winthrop 59, Liberty 50
article.story: LYNCHBURG, Va. (AP) -- Taj McCullough scored 14 points to lead Winthrop to a 59-50 victory Tuesday over Liberty in a Big South matchup. Liberty (13-12, 5-5 Big South) went on a 10-2 run in the first half to lead by nine points. Winthrop then went on a 10-3 run to draw even at 21 at halftime. Charles Corbin and Michael Jenkins each scored 10 points for Winthrop (16-9, 7-3), which pulled ahead to stay with 12:16 remaining, leading by as many as 12. Alex McLean scored 16 points and had 11 rebounds for Liberty.
